title: Dolapdere Big Gang - Local Strangers [2006]
description:
This is an album from the Turkish band "Dolpadere Big Gang". It includes Oriental covers from some of the most famous Rock & Pop songs:

- Can't Take My Eyes Off You
- Feel
- La isla Bonita
- Serenade
- Shut Up
- Billy Jean
- English Man in New York
- Enjoy The Silence
- It's Raining Men
- Losing My Religion
- Smoke on the Water
- Something Got Me Started

- The songs are MP3-128Kbps (i couldn't find a better quality) and it includes the Artwork

- It's a must-hear album, and i'm playing it non-stop in my car. if you like it, i suggest you to download "Rock El Casbah - Rachid Taha", which is also an Oriental Cover from the Algerian singer Rachid Taha.

- Please seed and comment after Downloading, i would like to have some feedback
